    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class can be used to solve the problem of multiple 3D objects alignment, by first collecting weighted links between pairs of points from different objects, and then solving for transformations minimizing weighted average of link penalties </para>
    </detaileddescription>
